**12) Webhooks vs App Messaging**
1. User-to-user app chat uses authenticated `/messages`.
2. Webhooks remain for external integrations and are protected by `WEBHOOK_TOKEN`.
3. Webhook paths can ingest events from providers/bots/other systems.

